If you would like to be on a mailing list that would notify you of changes
and additions to the manned station data within these directories,
particularly pertaining to the Palmer and Amundsen-Scott South Pole,
please send email to majordomo@ice.ssec.wisc.edu and leave the subject
line blank.  In the body of the message, type:

subscribe pole your@email.address

Substitute your real email address for "your@email.address" above. 
